name: Chief Retwin
Lore: 'Highly skilled saboteur. Former Imperial sympathizer who worked for the defense forces on his home planet, Ralltiir. Joined the Empire after Ralltiir''s subjugation.',
Text: 'May use 3 Force to ''hide'' (be excluded) from a battle. May use 2 Force to target one device or weapon present which deploys on a site. Draw destiny. If destiny > target''s deploy cost, target is lost.',
